Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(400,0)}[SAKURAMI塔 此刻]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪你相信誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}家族優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座塔對於我來說是充滿回憶之所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(400,0)}14年前 SAKURAMI塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年前的那一天 我被拋棄在這座塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸來這邊 快來快來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們很快就回來 在這邊乖乖等著哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很快就回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很快就回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很快就回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很快就回來」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天差勁透頂 那麼明天一定會比今天美好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是我們的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做戰場馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我一樣也是被父母拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼跟著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級教室在樓下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊學會自立吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在寫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寫馬克的事呀 說你又打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別一個勁盯著我 也多看看別的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看世界 看看你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好 沒有馬克就沒有現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在這裡舉行婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？在這麼偏僻的地方？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克把我差勁透頂的人生變得美好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(543,122)\shad0\3c&H838C86&\shad0}日記簿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\shad0\shad0\pos(293,247)\c&H8B8F8C&\3c&HFAFDFD&}馬克和學長打架了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\shad0\shad0\c&H8B8F8C&\3c&HFAFDFD&\pos(305,284)}就不能再老實一點嗎。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底搞什麼玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她搞什麼悲情角色扮演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 明明都有男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個誰吧 那個飛機頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 咱們要不要整她玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}我有重要的事和你說。 1個人到郊外那個廢棄工廠來  馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 馬克 快回話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 她還真來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有夠可愛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是說出去怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心放心 據說她沒有父母親人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想訴苦也沒地方說去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們還是未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}(收件-mail 我到廢棄工廠了哦。 你在哪裡？)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 為什麼不接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢工廠是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼覺得這麼不安
