Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:11.58,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3\fs23}翻譯 淺荷 十八 斑馬線  校譯 洛艾妖 時間 倉鼠  後期 風 壓制 風 追憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克痛苦的時候我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過的時候我陪你一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以不要丟下我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不會丟下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到這個世界的終結 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:11.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:01.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:13.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 就勞煩您大駕到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 爸爸他 居然騙了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 他們打算到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上面？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有辦法逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 12:45[櫻見塔 第一瞭望台] 由乃從7th那裡奪回了手機。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 12:48[櫻見塔 第一瞭望台] 發生爆炸。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用降落傘逃脫？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 13:02[櫻見塔 第一瞭望台] 7th他們拖著爸爸去了第二瞭望台。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 我們就打倒他們奪走降落傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你不是都輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在還受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我們失敗的原因顯而易見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小雪的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是二對一 所以輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 走吧 然後一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要按照自己的方法去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(400,0)}同時 「兒童養護設施 母親之家」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 櫻見塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了莫名其妙的爆炸起火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都有倒塌的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天野雪輝的病床上也留有「我們去櫻見塔」的字條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子可能會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去聯繫雪輝的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 8th的「服務器」也沒有找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這邊完全是個誘餌？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 他們追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說不要管什麼1st 趕快把未來日記破壞掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 看到軟弱的傢伙 就不自覺地管起閒事來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能在這座塔舉行婚禮太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠都會在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要徹底把他們打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的愛怎麼可能輸給他們那種虛偽的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st這次差不多也反省了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次估計會拚死一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們走吧 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太弱了 所以我藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我輸的理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我暴露在危險的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有在反省！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我上了 7th！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我上了 7th！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我上了」？你不是躲起來了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\pos(391,88)\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0}馬克和2nd開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(621,146)}刀從右邊向著臉刺來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(456,194)}小心啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(370,217)}馬克抓住了2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(460,329)}這樣的話只剩下1st了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(642,351)}不愧是馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(384,357)}馬克發現了1st的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 刀從右邊向臉刺來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！他會從右邊向你踢過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我這邊的刀快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透頂 別小看人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:00　小雪在父親和我之前選擇了我！今天說不定是我人生中最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:10 小雪在廣播室裡給我加油誒。我一定會好好努力給你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:20 小雪在廣播室裡。要好好的躲在那裡哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:30 小雪被7th抓住了！怎麼辦，得去救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:40 小雪跟7th對戰，受傷了。得趕緊治療。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st在廣播室麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把他抓回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的… 你們還真是不長教訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一怎麼可能贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 二對一不可能會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！1st！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日記顯示確實在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這個手機是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一是贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這個是我們所準備的假手機！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}13:20 愛因被1st用飛鏢破壞手機而死。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鏢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如由乃的作戰一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 快躲開飛鏢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被躲開了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是糟透了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天只會比今天更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克把最糟變成了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個降落傘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人就可以從塔裡逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以得到小雪的誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要奪取日記不就足夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這傢伙想殺了小雪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的做法老是這麼極端！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣就可以從這裡逃出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 結果還是沒能破壞掉手機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話借款還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九郎 你在做什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪怎麼樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被最麻煩的傢伙抓到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想辦法脫身的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去警局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不知道小雪發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在一起吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！ 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了放開我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全抬不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾呢 馬克已經從塌方里逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13：10 馬克和2nd戰鬥 右邊方向會有小刀飛向腦袋 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13: 20 馬克抓住了2nd 就只剩下1st了 不愧是馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:30 馬克找到了1st藏身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:40 馬克從塌方的地方逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:50 馬克好像受傷了 必須盡早包紮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的情況已經通過日記傳達給了外面的馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我快要死了的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們將葬身於這塔下的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克馬上就會從這脫身的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 就是馬克的勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你剁碎然後把外面的男人引進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會把這裡挖開的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別阻止我 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下這一條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這麼做了也無濟於事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就把你救出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要成為神 永遠在一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼我都要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 馬克 反正我都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這樣很好 繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是讓她住手的問題吧 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不弄髒自己的手 只會讓2nd保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼要人道之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話還真是不要臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我抬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 你給我在下面推一下啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是7th
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就正中由乃下懷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在不斷地保護你 殺死敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想把髒活累活都推到2nd身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 2nd你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少對我發號施令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼要保護1st
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻任意地扭曲1st的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不算是協助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自私
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該適可而止的是你 你這臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我是受到威脅才做這些的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我 我從一開始就沒想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 我馬上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會死？ 跟我沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西 給老子滾一邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我們的「愛」和你們的「愛」相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也中槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起把它抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你是真的喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是在暴走？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在缺乏信心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我信心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有趕上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz27.325\pos(604,372)\c&H4F5F4B&\3c&HCDDED4&\shad0}7th 美神 愛失血過多身亡 DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對敵人流露憐憫的眼神 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為神 兩人永遠在一起的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an8}7th 美神愛 失血過多身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an8)}馬克來救我了 果然還是馬克最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是永遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和爸爸媽媽好好說下的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會討厭爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有各種各樣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我希望爸爸媽媽重歸於好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望由乃能幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島警官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 在這個現場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島警官好像說了點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經聽不進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}(媽媽死了。)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君 你的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:42.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどのぐらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:42.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還將失去幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動を許される
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份悸動才將被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:53.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　焚くって涙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:53.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 焚燒之淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:59.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　降れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:59.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 如將滑落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:05.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来の繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:05.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都為緊系未來之鎖匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:12.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる体に傷目感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:12.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於崩壞之身中覺察那心傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:21.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度　君を　守ると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:21.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將再次 守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此立誓

Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:00 [櫻見市內某租賃公寓]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也去洗……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:23:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子才不知道她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪根蔥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？ 我是使魔之女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔女？！　馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要用這麼引人誤會的簡稱好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克終究也只不過是個下半身思考的野獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 我才不認識這女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給相親相愛的你們準備了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.31,0:24:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『交換日記』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是能讓你們倆人知曉對方未來的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:32.97,Note1,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:40\N我知道了馬克沒有劈腿。果然還是馬克最好了！\N4/21 19:23\N跑到陽台外面突然有隻貓飛撲過來。馬克，救命啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:32.97,Note2,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:40\N愛解開了對我的誤會。不愧是本大爺的女人。真有一套！\N4/21 19:23\N愛被貓纏住了。沒辦法，就讓本大爺來保護你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是馬克最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.47,0:24:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我眼中就只有你了 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.82,0:24:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倆人的愛到底是深還是淺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的男人和女人還真是複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不再通關一次遊戲來複習下吶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.48,0:25:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}串線
